						               													<description>While you are visiting the most amusement and dynamic travelling fair, you will have to collect as much tickets as possible. To make the most out of your stay, you will have to play some &amp;quot;fair&amp;rsquo;s games&amp;rdquo; and pile up the tickets of every booth before your opponents. Prevent your rivals from scoring, take their tickets away, challenge them and at the same time defend yourself from thieves and other attacks. Choose a strategy and hurry up to be the first one to reach the goal, but you have to be careful, because they will do everything in their hands so that it won&amp;rsquo;t be easy to reach it. Let&amp;rsquo;s get started!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each turn you either play a card or discard as many as you want, and then you replenish your hand to five cards again.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the fair you could find: &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     4 Different booths, which have to be placed in front of you as your collection, after that you will be able to get its 1, 2 or 3 card tickets.&amp;#10;     4 Types of tickets + the minstrel's tickets.&amp;#10;     The minstrel itself, whom could be doing any kind of roguery.&amp;#10;     2 Firamic crowns. First one to get each objective will receive a high ticket reward.&amp;#10;    4 &amp;quot;fair&amp;rsquo;s challenges&amp;rdquo;, which you will have to win playing with the golden cards every time in order to get the tickets. Everyone will offer you one of their cards and you could choose with whom you want to play against.&amp;#10;     A safety box, to protect your progress.&amp;#10;     Some candy, but you must be fast enough to get them! Last one to arrive will pay!&amp;#10;     And a thief ... and if you are lucky, maybe you could also find a security guard nearby for help.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Use your wit to create your own collection of booths, challenges and fill up your pockets with lots of tickets. It is recommended for a 2-4 player&amp;rsquo;s competition a goal of 20 tickets, and for a 5-6 player&amp;rsquo;s just 15 tickets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Is this rivalry going to separate or gather your family and friends?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
